STORY -
\b0 The Lab is deserted, but looks as if everyone is was just there. Also, it seems station wide comms are down, as you cannot hail Virgil. You need to get to Virgil central processing unit. After finding Virgil you attempt to report to the boss that no one is there, but comms are down. Several rooms associated with a certain researcher are missing(bed room, shower,Locker,office). Doors are missing to lower maintenance chambers. AFTER RESTARTING VIRGIL: Virgil's memory has been wiped regarding everything before your arrival. Virgil informs you that protocol dictates that you will need to find out what happened to the team while Virgil continues to attempt to get in contact with the main base. Virgil restores proper power and lighting to the area.\
\

