\b PUZZLES - \
	-
\b0 Get three security clearances(finger prints, retinal scan, and password) to enter Virgil Central Interface. You cannot register your own stuff, so you must get the security clearance from another researcher. To do this you must recover the Eye of the researcher, the finger of the researcher, and the researcher's password.\
\
	-Signal puzzle. As detailed by logs, several cryptic and surreal video signals have been broadcast throughout the station, having varying effects on the staff. The signal is actually an attempt by Locus to attempt to see if it can communicate with the researchers, and if they are of significant intelligence. The signals, combined with the information from the logs that clue you in on which signals belonged to which researcher, allowing you to guess the correct configuration of switches required to restart Virgil. 5 rows of 5 switches with modulation button\
