\i\b0 \ulnone Entry 2 -
\i0  I still cannot figure out why in the hell it just stopped. All the diagnostics suggested that the latest source code evolution should have improved geothermal gathering efficiencies by 0.25%. While promising, this is at best a modest gain, and according to my calculations this gene's fitness should still fall below the local maxima. There's simply no way it's topped off at this point. Perhaps if I go in and make some source code alterations by hand\'85.\
